The evidence with the title 'The American Middle Class is losing ground | Pew Research Center ' says Dec 9, 2015  ... After more than four decades of serving as the nation 's economic majority, the U.S. middle class is now matched in size by those in the economic tiers  ... Not kept pace with upper - income households, its median income, adjusted for household size , has risen over the long haul, increasing 34% since 1970. 
